article_id:759,category_name:News,title_name:Daily Free Tenfold Summons Are Here! Summon Up to 100 Times During the Event!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/fdbe5adea960e95742a1c8e3accb617f.png,message:<div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/fdbe5adea960e95742a1c8e3accb617f.png"></div><div>A daily free tenfold summon event, which will allow you to perform a tenfold summon on the applicable summon showcases for free once per day, started <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span>!<br><br>■Event Duration<br><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570427940"></span><br><br>■Applicable Summon Showcases<br>You can perform a tenfold summon on each of the following summon showcases for free once per day.<br><br>・Gala Dragalia<br>Note: You can perform up to seven tenfold summons during the seven-day period from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570168740"></span>.<br><br>・Fractured Futures<br>Note: You can perform up to three tenfold summons during the three-day period from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570168800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570427940"></span>.<br><br>Notes:<br>1. You can perform a tenfold summon for free on the applicable summon showcase once per day (each day is from 6:00 AM to 5:59 AM the next day).<br>2. The daily free tenfold summon resets each day at 6:00 AM.<br>3. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1569564000,update_time1569464755